channel.title: HELP! Servers going down down down
channel.description:
Please! Each time I try a server, it says:
"Error connecting to server. Must be down. Click cancel then.... "
Sometimes I can connect to a server, but it starts laggin in less than a minute and says "Connection lost, please.. "
What can I do !? Is this normal? I want to play on a server forever =( so i can train hard and make money etc etc
